Version 1.5.16
--------------
2011-06-22 erra <erra@ya.ru>
	* configure: PATH fixed for SunOS, echo -e for FreeBSD only
	* common/conversion.c: HAVE_ICONV_TRANSLIT applied
	* ircd/ircd.s: LOCPATH environment variable added for Linux
	* support/Makefile.in: custom locale installation added for Linux
	* support/configure.in: iconv detection fixed, message added for IPv6;
		zlib and ssl include/lib "found by compiler/linker" fixed
	* support/setup.h.in: USE_VHOST6, LOCALE_PATH added

2011-06-20 erra <erra@ya.ru>
	* configure: locale tests removed
	* contrib/uk_UA: proper locale packed for custom usage on Linux
	* support/locale_tests: patterns for testing locale added
	* support/setup.h.in: HAVE_ICONV_TRANSLIT added
	* support/configure.in: zlib, SSL and iconv detection reworked

Version 1.5.15
--------------
2011-06-17 erra <erra@ya.ru>
	* ircd/s_user.c: channel zmode check cancelled for collided nicks
		to avoid desync because of nickname protection by services
	* rusnet/rusnet_misc.c: rusnet_isagoodnickname() renamed to
		rusnet_zmodecheck() and optimized
	* support/config.h.dist: services nicks definitions reintroduced

