		in set_internal_encoding()

Version 1.5.10
--------------
2010-07-29 erra <erra@ya.ru>
	* common/support_ext.h, common/support.c: dgets() removed (obsoleted)
	* ircd/chkconf.c: mystrinclude() and simulateM4Include() removed
	* ircd/config_read.c: fileio.c include replaced with fileio.h include
	* ircd/s_misc.c: dgets() replaced with fgets() in read_motd() and
		read_rmotd()
	* ircd/fileio.c: moved to common/ (used in iserv)
	* ircd/fileio.h: renamed to common/fileio_ext.h (used in iserv)
	* ircd/s_externs.h: fileio_ext.h included
	* iserv/i_externs.h: fileio_ext.h included
	* iserv/iserv.c: dgets() replaced with fgets() in flushPendingLines()
	* support/Makefile.in: fileio.c compilation added

