Version 1.5.1
-------------
2010-07-02 LoSt <andrej@rep.kiev.ua>
	* common/support.c, common/support_ext.h, ircd/channel.c,
		ircd/s_conf.c, ircd/s_serv.c, ircd/s_service.c,
		ircd/s_user.c , ircd/whowas.c , ircd/whowas_def.h:
		Unicode userinfo handling fixed
	* common/conversion.c: RFC 2822 toupper/tolower conversion is now
		broken for {}| (not equal to []\ anymore) to match
		RusNet-1.4 behaviour

Version 1.5.0
-------------
2009-11-27 LoSt <andrej@rep.kiev.ua>
	* common/struct_def.h: buffer size increased for multibyte messages

1.5.0p20
2009-10-19 erra <erra@ya.ru>
	* common/bsd.c, common/bsd_ext.h: obsoleted and therefore removed
	* common/send_ext.h: obsoleted EXTERN declaration for deliver_it removed
	* ircd/s_user.c: tolerance to IPv6 IPs added for IPv4 only servers,
			ifdef RUSNET_RLINES in send_whois() taken beyond unrelated
			ifdef USE_OLD8BIT, control chars check reworked a bit

1.5.0p19
2009-09-25 erra <erra@ya.ru>
	* iauth/a_io.c: minus_one removed

