		Upgrade to this version is IMPORTANT to Services compatibility.


1.4.3_018 (R1_4_3_018 RC4)
2005-11-03 cj <cj@deware.com>
	* iserv/i_log.c: LOG_DAEMON changed to LOG_FACILITY in openlog() for
		syslog.

2005-11-02 cj <cj@deware.com> (from slcio <silence@irc.run.net>)
	* ircd/s_bsd.c: incorrect free_server() usage in connect_server():
		    serv linked list was not updated when connection failed.
		    This might cause infinite loops in m_server().

2005-11-01 cj <cj@deware.com>
	* ircd/ssl.c, s_bsd.c, ircd.c, ircd_ext.h: disconnection messages in
		    quit reason replaced with SSL onces, when IsSSL is true.
		    Small fix in ssl_fatal() has a chance to fix casual ssl 
		    disconnections.

